==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Post-fine
<hw>Post"-fine`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>post-</ets> + <ets>fine</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(O. Eng. Law)</fld>
<def>A duty paid to the king by the cognizee in a fine of lands, when
the same was fully passed; -- called also the <altname>king's
silver</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Postfix</ent>⟦br⟧
